## .gitignore
```gitignore
# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.pyo
venv/
env/
.env
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/

# VS Code
.vscode/
*.code-workspace

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# Logs
*.log
logs/

# Reports generated by the app
report-*.txt
scan-*.json

# API Keys (never commit these)
secrets.py
config.py
.env.local